[I] Tool to display AMDGPU usage

[T] amdgpu_top is tool that display AMD GPU utilization, like umr or
[T] clbr/radeontop or intel_gpu_top. The tool displays information gathered
[T] from performance counters (GRBM, GRBM2), sensors, fdinfo, and AMDGPU driver.

[U] https://github.com/Umio-Yasuno/amdgpu_top

